# Voice lines are bundled as resources/audio/tts/*.mp3.xz
# and do not require an API key during normal play.
#
# To regenerate voice lines after dialog changes (unchanged lines are skipped
# when their stored ttsTextSha256 matches the current ttsText):
#   ./"Highline Ridge" --refresh-voices=YOUR_XAI_API_KEY
#
# The API key is used only for that command and is not stored.